sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (uvicorn SSL)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / MySQL<br/>5432/TCP or 3306/TCP
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP or 9000/TCP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: External Client → MLflow API via Gateway

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Platform auth (gateway-level)
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)<br/>Forwarded Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443<br/>SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allow/Deny
    MLflow->>DB: TCP/5432 or TCP/3306<br/>TLS (optional, via CA bundle)<br/>Connection string credentials
    DB-->>MLflow: Query results
    MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: MLflow Artifact Upload via Serve-Artifacts

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>Artifact upload request
    Gateway->>MLflow: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca cert)<br/>Kubernetes Bearer Token
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443<br/>SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allow
    MLflow->>S3: HTTPS/443 or HTTP/9000<br/>TLS (via CA bundle)<br/>AWS IAM credentials (envFrom Secret)
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload acknowledgement
    MLflow-->>Gateway: Success response
    Gateway-->>Client: Success response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    Prometheus->>MLflow: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca cert, verified via<br/>openshift-service-ca.crt ConfigMap)<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    MLflow-->>Prometheus: Metrics response
